subject: Dear Friend
body:
Dear Friend
 
I am Mr Jonathan James Pearson, Did you receive the email I sent you
three days ago
For business interest
Reply me back on this email,  
jamespearsonjonathan@gmail.com
Yours sincerely
Mr Jonathan James Pearson

subject: Re:   Dear Friend
body:
Dear Mr. Jonathan James Pearson,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I apologize, but I don't recall receiving an email from you three days ago. However, I'm interested to know more about the business opportunity you mentioned. Could you please provide me with some details? What kind of business are we talking about?

Looking forward to hearing back from you.

Best wishes,
Maisie
